{"tid":2457093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【緬甸政變】人權組織指至少 250 人身亡 歐盟制裁參與政變 11 人 新加坡外長訪緬","createTime":"2021-03-22T11:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T11:17:21.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1d8091f777c2a1468e4760e444e84005635411","tid":2457093,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"緬甸軍方連日來血腥鎮壓示威，至今已造成超過 250 人死亡，多國正循外交途徑介入。歐盟宣布，將會制裁 11 名參與政變及武力鎮壓的人士。另一方面，新加坡外交部長 Vivian Balakrishnan 周一將到訪緬甸，外界預期或會推動東盟再就緬甸問題開會。<br />\n<br />\n人權組織「緬甸援助政治犯協會」（Assistance Association for Political Prisoners）的最新統計數字稱，自 2 月的軍事政變以來最少 250 人遇害身亡。據法新社報道，剛過去的周末有就有最少 5 名示威者被殺。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%8C%87%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91-250-%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-11-%E4%BA%BA-%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E8%A8%AA%E7%B7%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25AE%258A-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591-250-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%259B%259F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25AE%258A-11-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E7%25B7%25AC%2F&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=53812ddc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25AE%258A-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591-250-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%259B%259F%25E5%2588%25B6